<![CDATA[<p>Filed under: <a href="http://japanese.engadget.com/category/peripherals/" rel="tag">周辺機器</a>, <a href="http://japanese.engadget.com/category/cellphones/" rel="tag">携帯電話</a></p><div style="text-align: center;"><img vspace="4" hspace="4" border="0" src="http://www.blogcdn.com/japanese.engadget.com/media/2011/04/maxellqi.jpg"  alt="" /></div>
